      </task>
      <task workspace="3cm" xml:id="act-8-4-1-task-1">
        <statement>
          <p>
            Plot the sequence of partial sums from part (a).
            What do you notice about this sequence?
          </p>
        </statement>
        <hint/>
        <answer>
          <p>
            There appears to be a limit for the sequence of partial sums.
          </p>
        </answer>
        <solution>
          <p>
            The entries in the sequence of partial sums from part (a) is shown in the figure below.
          </p>
          <p>
            Notice that the partial sums seem to oscillate back and forth around some fixed number,
